<html lang="en">
<head>
</head>
<body>
<%= image_tag("#{APP_URL}/images/email_signature.jpg", :alt=>"SitterScout.com") %>

<font face="Arial, Helvetica, Geneva">

<p>Dear <%= @parent.profile.full_name %>,</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder from SitterScout that <%= @sitter.profile.full_name %> is scheduled to babysit for you on <%= @job.date_from.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> from <%= @job.date_from.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> to <%= @job.date_to.strftime("%I:%M %p") %>. Enjoy your break!</p>

<p>If you have friends who could use a faster and easier way to find a babysitter, click <%= link_to "here", APP_URL + "/parents/#{@parent.id}/invite_friends" %> to tell them about SitterScout.</p>

<p>The SitterScout Team</p>
</font>
</body>
</html>